TITLE: useMouse hook for cursor tracking
DESCRIPTION: This React hook, `useMouse`, tracks the mouse's position and its position relative to a specific HTML element.  It uses `useLayoutEffect` to ensure that the measurements are taken after the layout is complete. It returns the current mouse state and a ref to the element.
