TITLE: Applying Splat to Fluid in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This function applies a splat to the fluid simulation at the specified coordinates with the given velocity (dx, dy) and color. It binds the splat program, sets uniforms for target, aspect ratio, point, color, and radius, and then blits the result to the velocity and dye textures.
