TITLE: Update Pointer Move Data
DESCRIPTION: This function updates the pointer's data during a mouse or touch movement. It sets the previous texture coordinates, calculates new texture coordinates based on the current position, calculates the delta values, sets the moved flag, and assigns a color to the pointer.
