TITLE: Calculating Delta Time in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This function calculates the delta time (dt) between the current frame and the last frame. It limits the maximum dt to 0.016666 seconds to prevent issues with large time steps.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ui-layouts/cursify/blob/main/content/components/fluid-cursor.mdx#_snippet_33

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
function calcDeltaTime() {
  let now = Date.now();
  let dt = (now - lastUpdateTime) / 1000;
  dt = Math.min(dt, 0.016666);
  lastUpdateTime = now;
  return dt;
}
```

