SOURCE: https://github.com/ui-layouts/cursify/blob/main/content/components/fluid-cursor.mdx#_snippet_57

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
function wrap(value, min, max) {
  const range = max - min;
  if (range == 0) return min;
  return ((value - min) % range) + min;
}
```

